latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Such an amazing opportunity to be Lead artist on @spacenk latest Christmas campaign with influencer @wishwishwish 

I had the privilege of working with @wishwishwish to design and create her stunning looks featured in the campaign. The 2 day weekend was an absolute dream and I’m very honoured to have been given the opportunity to be a part of the production of this incredible advert! 

I could not have done it without @madelinerowlandmua @matildecaprilli who both assisted me on this project and did a phenomenal job creating the makeup looks for all of the guests. 

It was also so lovely to meet, work and assist @cattfindley with set design. She did an incredible job 🤩

And what a honour it was to work with and watch @miguelsantana_  work his magic to film and produce such beautiful visual content 😍
